==English==

===Noun===
'''[[plume]] [[moth]]'''
# {{zoology}} Any one of numerous small, slender moths, belonging to the family ''Pterophoridae''. Most of them have the wings deeply divided into two or more [[plumelike]] [[lobe]]s. Some species are [[injurious]] to the [[grapevine]].

